# HUD::SET_TEXT_EDGE

## Summary
Draws an outline round the entire text

## Parameters
* **INT** edgeAmount
* **INT** red
* **INT** green
* **INT** blue
* **INT** alpha

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
This native does absolutely nothing, just a nullsub
